Package herencia

Class Enrollment

  • java.lang.Object
    • herencia.Enrollment
  • public class Enrollment
extends java.lang.Object
    The Enrollment class represents an enrollment entity that manages a collection of students, courses, and the institution they are enrolled in. This class provides constructors, getter and setter methods for each property, and a toString method for easy representation of an Enrollment object.
